title: i just won my final promo game
body:
So i win my final promo game and it apparently never happened, as in i was 1/1 in bronze 5 and i just won my final game and it hasn't counted riot pls help

Edit 1: checking match history my second promo game isn't there either, according to my in client history all 3 promo games are there, but according to the website match history i have only played 1 game of promos?

replies.body: Match history has been taking ages to show my last games recently, Saw it on a mates account too.
sometimes it takes a while to register in the system, wait an hour or two, or maybe check now.
